{
  "stem": "19969.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They know what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I've never been able to find Lieutenant Strickland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the company commander, Lieutenant Walsh, is very much alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He lives in Pennsylvania.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was a commander who was there and saw the whole thing, along with a large number of his men and some of my men as well.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the strange thing about the investigation, some of the witnesses testified that I was the one who stopped the shooting with a machine gun.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So no charges were filed against me, apparently for that reason.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But about four or five of my men were-- five, I think, about three or four from the 42nd Division that participated in the killing of those five guards were charged with murder, which is a very serious offense, of course a general court martial.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Well, it was, I say, illuminating to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because now I have been able to put together all of the pieces and know exactly what happened.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The 42nd Division says I make up all these things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I made up all this stuff.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Well, I was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I didn't make up anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I didn't have to make up anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So that's the way it is today.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But they're still claiming that, and they're writing nasty letters to the Department of History and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I don't give a damn myself who liberated it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I'm sorry that I was ever there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The only comfort we got out of that whole incident was that we were able to free several thousand poor souls who would-- were dying daily before our arrival.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So many of them, at least, were able to resume some out of a halfway normal life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I have met several of them who were there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Some live here in Denver.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
